OL,6,FThousands are expected to take part in
OL,7,Fanti-tourism protests in the .
OL,9,Fis one of the most popular
OL,10,Fdestinations for British tourists, but
OL,11,Fthe country is struggling to cope with
OL,12,Fthe influx of visitors.
OL,14,FResidents of the popular holiday
OL,15,Fdestination say too much tourism is
OL,16,Fdamaging the environment, driving down
OL,17,Fwages and squeezing locals out of the
OL,18,Fhousing market. Some are sleeping in
OL,19,Ftheir cars or even in caves.
