OL,3,CThousands across Canary Islands to
OL,4,Cprotest tourism
OL,6,Fas part of a wider campaign demanding
OL,7,Fthe Canary Islands government tackle
OL,8,Fthe effects of excess tourism in the
OL,9,Fregion.
OL,11,FHundreds of people linked arms to form
OL,12,Fa human chain to demonstrate against
OL,13,Fthe building of an additional hotel
OL,14,Fand beach resort, as well as future
OL,15,Fprojects aimed at attracting more
OL,16,Ftourists. The hunger strike was still
OL,17,Funderway on Wednesday at the time of
OL,18,Fwriting.
