OL,3,CThousands across Canary Islands to
OL,4,Cprotest tourism
OL,6,FThe wider movement is called Canarias
OL,7,FSe Agota, which means 'The Canaries
OL,8,FHave Had Enough'.
OL,10,FIn an Instagram post the organisation
OL,11,Fsaid the Canary Islands are
OL,12,F"exhausted" because of the "excessive
OL,13,Ftourism" and the "lack of attention to
OL,14,Fthe basic needs of the population".
